Package users

Interface IUser

All Known Subinterfaces:
IStaffMember, IStudent
All Known Implementing Classes:
Staff, Student, User
public interface IUser
Interface defining the base contract for all users in the system. Provides methods for managing common user attributes such as ID, name, email, department, and course information. This interface serves as the foundation for specific user types (e.g., students, staff) in the system.
